<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width">
    <title><%= htmlWebpackPlugin.options.title %></title>
    <style id="colors"></style>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=IBM+Plex+Serif" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="content">
        <div class="box">
            <h1 class="text-color">David Henderson - Web Developer</h1>
            
            <blockquote>
                    There is a real danger that computers will develop intelligence and take over. We urgently need to develop direct connections to the brain so that computers can add to human intelligence rather than be in opposition. 
                    <cite>Stephen Hawking</cite>
            </blockquote>

            <p>The theme of this site is entirely generated by machine learning.</p>
            <input id="brain-button" type="submit" value="Brain it!">

            <label for="background-color">
                    Style:
                    <input type="color" id="choose-color">
            </label>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="controls" style="display: none;">
        <label for="background-color">
            Background Colour:
            <input type="color" id="background-color">
        </label><br>
        <label for="text-color">
            Text Color:
            <input type="color" id="text-color">
        </label><br>
        <input id="save-colors" type="submit" value="I Love it!">
    </div>

   
</body>
</html>
